name: Symbol of Virtue and Devotion: PISCES
description: Deciding to erase beauty and love from the earth, Typhon decides to come to Olympus. Typhon, whom even the gods fear Hermes, the messenger of the gods, announces this visit to the other gods. His suggestion is to disguise himself to protect himself from Typhon.Hermes transforms himself into a heron. Learning of this war to destroy themselves, Aphrodite and her son Eros,ın order to cross the Nile, they change into a pair of fish.
